

GULPI

   This word is from the Spanish golpe.

   gulpí
   to beat up

   gulpí
   to hit, to strike

   ginulpi ng pulis
   beat up by police

   Ginulpi nila ako.
   They beat me up.

   The Commission on Filipino Language is currently advocating gulpé as
   the standard spelling.

   gulpehín, mánggulpé (gulpihin, manggulpi)
